<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Are you interested in tackling the deepest, most enduring questions faced by humankind? Philosophers develop skills in logic, reasoning, and argument to face challenging problems, from social, political, and religious issues to the problem of consciousness and the paradoxes of infinity.</p>
